      "body": "Google introduced Gemini 3 on November 18, 2025, establishing new standards in multimodal reasoning by natively processing diverse data types including text, images, video, audio, and code (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGeBZ94dmxUZWazUPZPCyBP5ET-I332z-Q9KGuPl0wZUUtu_SlIcRFE9M9jxmP5WflE0eFcDssojx0_1xYTbUDiR3GTDuu2aVaVrEinzem9Ri9Ftu9-kcJ6y-fNgCJ-I_s7qwtNpN1yeISbmmsip12BzA==). This model now leads major reasoning benchmarks and features a 'Deep Research mode' for complex scientific investigations (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGeBZ94dmxUZWazUPZPCyBP5ET-I332z-Q9KGuPl0wZUUtu_SlIcRFE9M9jxmP5WflE0eFcDssojx0_1xYTbUDiR3GTDuu2aVaVrEinzem9Ri9Ftu9-kcJ6y-fNgCJ-I_s7qwtNpN1yeISbmmsip12BzA==). Concurrently, Isomorphic Labs, a DeepMind spinout, advanced AlphaFold 3-designed oncology candidates into human trials, showcasing atomic-accuracy prediction of protein-ligand interactions (https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGeBZ94dmxUZWazUPZPCyBP5ET-I332z-Q9KGuPl0wZUUtu_SlIcRFE9M9jxmP5WflE0eFcDssojx0_1xYTbUDiR3GTDuu2aVaVrEinzem9Ri9Ftu9-kcJ6y-fNgCJ-I_s7qwtNpN1yeISbmmsip12BzA==).",
